    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This example has been properly sorted for the enthusiast, with the high-pressure VANOS unit recently serviced and the rear subframe reinforced to ensure structural rigidity. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential that remains tight. Suspension geometry is true, utilizing refreshed bushings for a communicative chassis. While the exterior shows honest signs of spirited use, the internal mechanicals are robust, featuring consistent compression across all cylinders and a proactively refreshed cooling system. A visceral, turn-key driver's car.",
